[{"location":"cubic/#Cubic-Lattice","page":"CubicLattice","title":"Cubic Lattice","text":"Build a cubit lattice:\n\nusing CairoMakie\nusing SimpleLattices\nL = CubicLattice(2, 3, 4, true, true, true)\n\nGet the edges of the lattice:\n\nedges(L)\n\nPlot the lattice:\n\nplot_lattice(L)","category":"section"},{"location":"square/#Square-Lattice","page":"SquareLattice","title":"Square Lattice","text":"Build a cubit lattice:\n\nusing CairoMakie\nusing SimpleLattices\nL = SquareLattice(7, 5, true, true)\n\nGet the edges of the lattice:\n\nedges(L)\n\nPlot the lattice:\n\nplot_lattice(L)","category":"section"},{"location":"#SimpleLattices","page":"Home","title":"SimpleLattices","text":"Documentation for SimpleLattices.\n\n","category":"section"},{"location":"#SimpleLattices.CubicLattice-Tuple{Int64, Int64, Int64}","page":"Home","title":"SimpleLattices.CubicLattice","text":"CubicLattice(Nx::Int, Ny::Int, Nz::Int; xperiodic::Bool=false, yperiodic::Bool=false, zperiodic::Bool=false)\n\nCreate a cubic lattice with Nx sites in the x-direction, Ny sites in the y-direction, and Nz sites in the z-direction. By default, the lattice is not periodic in any direction. Set xperiodic=true, yperiodic=true, or zperiodic=true to make it periodic in the respective direction.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#SimpleLattices.SquareLattice-Tuple{Int64, Int64}","page":"Home","title":"SimpleLattices.SquareLattice","text":"SquareLattice(Nx::Int, Ny::Int; xperiodic::Bool=false, yperiodic::Bool=false)\n\nCreate a square lattice with Nx sites in the x-direction and Ny sites in the y-direction. By default, the lattice is not periodic in either direction. Set xperiodic=true or yperiodic=true to make it periodic in the respective direction.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#SimpleLattices.plot_lattice-Tuple{AbstractLattice}","page":"Home","title":"SimpleLattices.plot_lattice","text":"plot_lattice(lattice::AbstractLattice)\n\nPlot the given lattice. Using GLMakie or CairoMakie if available. Returns a figure.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"triangular/#Triangular-Lattice","page":"TriangularLattice","title":"Triangular Lattice","text":"Build a cubit lattice:\n\nusing CairoMakie\nusing SimpleLattices\nL = TriangularLattice(7, 5, true, true)\n\nGet the edges of the lattice:\n\nedges(L)\n\nPlot the lattice:\n\nplot_lattice(L)","category":"section"}]
